ITV.Tour.de.France.2014.Stage.19.Highlights.PDTV.x264-NX

Friday 25th July 2014 ITV4
7pm to 8pm Highlights

Highlights of stage 19 - out of the mountains and the riders are finally allowed to take a breather. This 208km stage between Maubourguet and Bergerac is a flat one and will be a game of cat-and-mouse between the breakaway and the sprinters' teams all day. Presented by Gary Imlach with analysis from Chris Boardman, commentary by Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen with Ned Boulting the reporter at the roadside.
